text: Caliber 9 () is a 1972 Italian crime movie directed by Fernando Di Leo and stars Gastone Moschin, Barbara Bouchet, Mario Adorf, Frank Wolff, Luigi Pistilli, Ivo Garrani and Lionel Stander. ==Other websites== * Category:1972 crime movies Category:Italian crime movies Category:Movies directed by Fernando Di Leo
